Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It's all squirmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? An alien umbilical cord?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that put it in, you eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young ones, you mustn't waste food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu, you put chocolate in the damn napkins, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-san, you put in beer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught me?\N But it deepens the flavor, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already so deep I can't tell what tastes like what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but may I open the curtain for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, as always, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what kind of training is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what the future holds in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must take that endless bit of darkness and turn it to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is practical training for doing just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking it in the dark, it's not like beer at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-san is a mysterious dental hygienist who comes and goes under Master Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lives on ethyl alcohol and Castellas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has a habit of getting drunk and licking people's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're drinking with Hanuki-san, you'd better be prepared for an endless night of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was once freely dragged all around Kiyamachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I came to I was collapsed near the Ebisugawa power plant all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ozu was a person without even a single point of praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could eat three helpings of people's misfortune.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although only 15 minutes earlier than me, he's Master Higuchi's first disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H000001&\3c&H6C362A&\be3}"Arrogant"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H000001&\3c&H6C362A&\be3}"Selfish"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\c&H000001&\3c&H6C362A&\be3}"Lazy"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\c&H000001&\3c&H6C362A&\be3}"Perverse"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he takes glory in this meaningless lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't Akashi-san come?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she has a report she can't get out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report I can't get out of too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, after neglecting my studies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and spending all day "training" for things, surrounded by these worthless faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have made a complete mess of my first two years of college life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question that must be put to the person responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Where is the one responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(640,470)\bord0\fad(400,0)}"Will the responsible party come forward!" 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H6C00C6&\fad(200,0)}J{\c&H000000&}-pwq
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before me lay open countless doors to that rose-colored campus life.  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, at that time I had a bad premonition.  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,1000)\bord0\c&H1B2E1F&}"Disciples Wanted"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I could not envision
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those suspicious-looking fliers leading to some glorious future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not reach out for these fliers!  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I should get as far away as possible!  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I was not able to escape.  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,100)\bord0\c&H1B2E1F&}"Disciples Wanted"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the clairvoyance to pick out fair maidens from the crowds of Gion,  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the devil's ears that let not even the sound of sakura falling into the canals slip past,  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Higuchi Seitarou!  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, ye youths of limitless possibility!  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad premonition was right on the mark.  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I held a position of not opening up my heart to anyone,  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as Master Higuchi lived in Yuusuisou, the same boarding house as I, we hit it off,  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36\pos(100,60)\bord1.2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\be4\fad(200,200)}"'Myself' is over 20 years old.\N Ozu did not imbibe."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fact that I was just old enough to drink helped immediately...  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long the walls came down and I was enjoying myself.  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result of our heated arguments over boobs until dawn...  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is not whether it is real breast or not.  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is whether you believe it.  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch, on!  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I ended up becoming his second disciple.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that was the only time our Master ever treated us to alcohol.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being the disciple of Higuchi Seitarou...  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not clear as to what I'm a disciple in even after these two years.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you looked under the cover,  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Higuchi was no hermit-master or anything, but just some eighth-year student.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how animals that live long lives feel somewhat uncanny,  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our master had this mysterious air about him unlike a normal person's.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wore the same yukata and tall geta everywhere he went all year round,  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he knew 100 places to cool off in the summer.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't speak anything other than Japanese  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but could converse cordially with people in any country,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there were times he perceived things that normal people did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body was light, and incredible.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, he didn't participate in anything,  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only focusing intently on living life day-to-day.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His was a frighteningly gentlemanly manner, perhaps the pinnacle of buffoonery.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he had a weakness.  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had library fines.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Master was being targeted  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by a secret collection organization known as the Library Police.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping him escape from them was our duty as his disciples.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fiend!  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides the Library Police, Master also had an ongoing battle with a man named Jougasaki.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What color?  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pink.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master called this battle the "Masochistic Proxy-Proxy War."  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as the name implies, it was a "war" of the tiniest,  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pettiest, stupidest things you could imagine.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that five years ago there was some deep strife between the two  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which caused the opening shots to be fired.  
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.97,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we, as his disciples, were wrapped up in this pointless struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(1218,566)\bord0\c&HEFF4F2&}"Glued"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, when we had 20 plates of sushi delivered,  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd invite over a bunch of exchange students for a sushi party  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and me and Ozu would split the bill.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it was always us who got the short end of the stick.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if wasting my precious youth helping with this stuff was a good thing,  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but each day and the next I worked hard to pay him back.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaori!  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki is a perverted man the same year as Master Higuchi  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the head of the movie circle,  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's still uncertain what grudge they have between them.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The journey is over.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\c&H000104&}"Goal"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the chaos just after the war in the Pacific,  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,med students that stole the technique  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,behind tortoise-shaped scrubbing brushes from Nishio Market  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,created a mystical cleaning weapon from the fibers of a palm that grew in Taiwan.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tips of the fiber were both stiff and supple;  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seemingly used the Van der Waals force to bind dirt particles.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so this company was put under pressure by detergent makers for fear of losing sales.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As its power to clean was considered too great a threat, it was banished to the depths of history;  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}However, seems like someone continues to make them even now, in secret.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to obtain one of these mystical tortoise scrubbing brushes.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30\bord1\be1\fad(400,400)\pos(105,345)}"Demachi Futaba Mame-mochi"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is another part of your training.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fs30\bord1\be1\fad(400,400)\pos(1252,538)}"Shuugoin\N Nama\N Yatsuhashi"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs30\bord1\be1\fad(400,0)\pos(430,540)}"Nishimura\N Eisei\N Boro"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.73,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our master has required many things prior to this, and we were always supplying him.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30\bord1\be1\fad(400,0)\pos(1208,44)}"Ox-drawn cart of ancient pine"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs34\bord1\be1\fad(400,0)}"Ueda Sweets Factory Conpa-Rusk"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs34\bord1\be1\fad(400,0)\pos(100,378)}"Remembrance of Kamesuehiro"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs34\bord1\be1\fad(400,0)}"Ueno Liquor Shop Tsubame Sauce"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fs34\bord1\be1\fad(400,0)\pos(1112,601)}"Nishiri Senmai-zuke"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final test.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do whatever you can to get it by tomorrow at noon.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you're expelled.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I thought of it while cleaning the 4.5 tatami room,  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's something I did wish could be made a reality.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master's room was so dirty that at just that one glance,  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a lady of sheltered upbringing would surely swoon. It was a disaster.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HEED3D9&}"Never heard of it"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised if it was some life form  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HE1E8DA&}"You don't plan to buy anything?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H9784D9&}"Are you makin' fun of me, idiot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that had never previously existed on the Earth's surface that secretly evolved.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H9885D9&}"Hey, bring the salt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming all the way to the Sanjou Bridge,\N as it was lunch time, I saw fish and onions lined up.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd rather shoot fireworks at them,  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I had a feeling like I'd already done that,  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which made my uneasiness all the more indescribable.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to I had moved to Kiyamachi,  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and despite it still being mid-day, an old fortune teller was spreading out her eerie aura.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fortunes of this creature must surely be spot on.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back?  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, back?  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are unsatisfied.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you have fiercely earnest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tip my hat to the old woman's insight.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I feel there's an opportunity you can't let slip away.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the opportunity dangling in front of your eyes.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 4,000 yen.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}This is getting more and more abridged.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our master made us do all kinds of meaningless things in the name of "training," 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and most of them made no sense.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought a countless number of times, "Why am I doing this?"  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't help but think, "If only I hadn't met the Master..."  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why shouldn't I just expel myself?  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san is a first year in the engineering\N department like Ozu, and a younger disciple.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mystical tortoise scrubbing brush?  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if it actually exists.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us search!  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man I'd asked before, who was like a boiled octopus,  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,acted nice like he'd just found Princess Kaguya in a bamboo shoot.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who runs a general store in West Kinichiba might know something.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the owner of the general store facing Bukkouji road.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who runs the old book store over there might know something.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The used utensil shop in Shinkyougoku might know.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san was quite skilled at information-gathering,  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and narrowed down the location of the tortoise.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're searching for the mystical tortoise scrubbing brush.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about the mystical...  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Higuchi.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how much for it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I will ask 100,000 yen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I'm buying that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No scrubbing brush is worth 100,000 yen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you'd wash in a sink of a 4.5 tatami boarding house covered in sludge. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough. I give up on the scrubbing brush. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally expelled. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Master is not going to cut the thread so trivially. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will ask him as well. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:32.95,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(100,100)}If I can become a circle with you... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\c&H1575B2&\3c&H000214&\pos(1150,360)}"At the\N public\N bath"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:40.83,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(100,100)}Farewell triangle; I'll come back sometime, square.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:49.37,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(100,0)}Circle X triangle... Always a dead space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:57.45,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(0,100)}The world tends to 4 sides, 4 faces, 5 sides, 6 sides, turkey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:02.24,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(100,100)\t(1,\3c&HA99263&)}Search for the circle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:06.30,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(100,100)\3c&HA99263&}Search for the circle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.82,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(100,0)\3c&HA99263&}To learn how not to become a circle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:15.03,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\3c&HA99263&}It might be nowhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:18.33,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(0,100)\3c&HA99263&}It might be somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:22.91,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(100,0)\3c&HA99263&}You don't know either...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:29.42,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(0,0)\3c&HA99263&\t(1,\3c&H041337&)}On this Kamo River.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:33.42,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2}Search for the circle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:37.93,IOSYS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1\be2\fad(0,400)}Search for the circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was listening to my Master's song, 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly had a feeling like he would be going somewhere far away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi-kun and Jougasaki-kun were here earlier. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had been a long time since they'd met. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-san's pretty cool, isn't he? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Higuchi-kun is all that different, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-kun hasn't had any other friends than Higuchi-kun since long ago. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think that Higuchi-kun is going to make you his successor. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been expelled. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't think I'm suited to living in such a shrewd manner. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all began when two high school seniors were rivals in love. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that it was a drinking contest with unrefined sake, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the details are already lost to the depths of history. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so this battle dragged on for a long time, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they refused to let it drop without coming to a conclusion. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in their utter desperation, they thought up the Proxy War. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They forgot the reason for the battle's beginning, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and, without regard to changes in society, passed it down through successors. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Technically it's called the Masochistic Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy- 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-\NProxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy War. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we talking about this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking it over, see. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came back, there was a bag left in my room I did not know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funds for continuing the Proxy War? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's what anymore. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was precisely the amount of money needed to buy the tortoise brush! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take the Eizan Electric up to Kurama and hide it near Ushiwakamaru? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I take the Kyoto-Osaka and head around Naniwa with some raven-haired maidens? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was called Mochiguman, and Akashi-san had once told me she had lost it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they come in sets of five and she lost one. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please grab the opportunity that is dangling in front of you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HBB00E6&\3c&HF6EFF6&\be3}"A Dream Date with Akashi-san"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let myself be expelled! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this 100,000 yen I should return to the life I deserve! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this you have cleared the final test! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I did everything the Master said these past two years just to see this smile. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a ceremony now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I have something important to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dual on the Kamooohashi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Proxy-Proxy War will continue with you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you two. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see this through. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's go. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the cannons were readied for the decisive battle. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki came walking from the Nishimusubu side. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two soon met in the center of the Kamooohashi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akashi-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again. How are you feeling? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'm fit and healthy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are one of the Higuchi's? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I became his disciple last fall. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And isn't that my disciple, Ozu? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my proxy, the one who will succeed me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have thought he was your disciple, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was actually my spy, you see. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I fool you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that, Master. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:18:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is unprecedented in the history of the Masochistic Proxy-Proxy War. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name will be etched into history. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things sure dragged out for a long time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it five years? Or more? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've forgotten. It's been a battle of so many years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu was active in all fields, and despite filming a hit-piece on Jougasaki, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems he also dyed Master Higuchi's yukata pink, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and played the part of a meaningless double agent. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy is your proxy? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it over with already! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle started with such a flat phrase. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a moment's breath the two clashed! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock-Paper-Scissors! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's over! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-kun won, so Ozu-kun goes first next! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weight has finally been lifted from my shoulders. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving on a journey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hanuki. Higuchi is spouting some nonsense. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I plan on circling the globe once. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with me, Hanuki? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can speak English, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy. This is foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have money? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the prize money from the Shimanami Cup. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, sorry about this,\N but please clean up the room with this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so my Master disappeared with the wind. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go out for a drink? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally in the mood? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who spends all that money on your love-doll. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn about that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-kun. He tells me everything. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that little... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is his real story anyway? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might rather jump into the Kamo River. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe run away from Kyoto to Murotomisaki and obtain enlightenment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to our time together... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize if you were supposed to bat first. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue to play nice and dirty. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first shot of the Proxy-Proxy War had been fired. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being caught by Master Higuchi in front of that clock tower 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was surely a turning point in my fate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had joined some other circle, I would have surely spent quite a different two years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly meeting Ozu was my greatest mistake.
